snippet.title: One Beat Min - Teaser
snippet.description:
Explosive, Stylish, and Energetic 2D Rhythm/Fighting game about Beatbox Battles.

One Beat Min puts players in the role of an up-and-coming musical master battling rivals full of personality in a hip-hop world moved by the beat.
